# Environment Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual API keys

# Primary API: Get your API key from https://financialmodelingprep.com/
# Free tier: 250 calls/day
FMP_API_KEY=your_fmp_api_key_here

# Backup API: Get your API key from https://twelvedata.com/
# Free tier: 800 calls/MONTH (~25/day - used only as emergency fallback)
